          "alias": "featurePropertyFeatureTitle",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Sights"
        },
        {
          "alias": "richTextContent",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": {
            "blocks": {
              "contentData": [],
              "settingsData": [],
              "expose": [],
              "Layout": {}
            },
            "markup": "\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESpa town of Chianciano Terme\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EGuided tour of Abbey of Monte Olivieto Maggiore\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EPienza\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EChurch of Madonna Di San Biagio, Montepulciano\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAssisi \u0026amp; guided tour of the frescoes at Basilica of St Francis\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EPerugia \u0026amp; Galleria Nazionale dell\u2019 Umbria\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESiena \u0026amp; guided tour of the Opera del Duomo\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESan Gimignano\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EFlorence \u0026amp; the Uffizi\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EPisa or Orvieto\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
